Class Fish

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.csupomona.cs.cs141.prog_assgmnt_4.Animal
      • edu.csupomona.cs.cs141.prog_assgmnt_4.Fish
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Fish
extends Animal
    The Fish object is a subclass of Animal, so it will inherit all of it's fields and methods. The Fish will have 5 different variety's of fish type, which will help make each fish distinct.
    Author:
    David Scianni
